#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:2
msgid "SpeQtrum"
msgstr "SpeQtrum"

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:4
msgid ""
"The :mod:`~qilisdk.speqtrum` package provides an optional, synchronous "
"client for the Qilimanjaro SpeQtrum cloud. Through the "
":class:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum` class you can authenticate, "
"inspect devices and jobs, and submit digital, analog, or pulse "
"experiments for remote execution."
msgstr ""
"El paquete :mod:`~qilisdk.speqtrum` proporciona un cliente sincrónico "
"opcional para la nube SpeQtrum de Qilimanjaro. A través de la clase "
":class:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum` se puede autenticar, "
"inspeccionar dispositivos y trabajos, y enviar experimentos digitales, "
"analógicos o de pulso para su ejecución remota."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:9
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Instalación"

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:11
msgid ""
"SpeQtrum support is shipped as an optional dependency group. Install it "
"alongside QiliSDK with:"
msgstr ""
"El soporte de SpeQtrum se distribuye como un grupo de dependencias "
"opcional. Instálelo junto con QiliSDK con:"

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:18
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "Autenticación"

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:20
msgid ""
"The API uses short-lived OAuth tokens that are cached in the system "
"keyring. Call :meth:`SpeQtrum.login "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.login>` once and the credentials will"
" be reused for subsequent sessions."
msgstr ""
"La API utiliza tokens OAuth de corta duración que se almacenan en caché "
"en el llavero del sistema. Llame a :meth:`SpeQtrum.login "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.login>` una vez y las credenciales se"
" reutilizarán en sesiones posteriores."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:42
msgid "Client Construction"
msgstr "Construcción del Cliente"

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:44
msgid ""
"Once credentials are stored, instantiate "
":class:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum` to start issuing requests. "
"Construction fails with a ``RuntimeError`` if no cached credentials "
"exist."
msgstr ""
"Una vez almacenadas las credenciales, instancie "
":class:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum` para comenzar a emitir "
"solicitudes. La construcción falla con un ``RuntimeError`` si no existen "
"credenciales en caché."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:55
msgid "Device Catalogue"
msgstr "Catálogo de Dispositivos"

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:57
msgid ""
"Devices are represented by "
":class:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.Device` models containing the "
"device code, number of qubits, hardware type, and status. Use "
":meth:`SpeQtrum.list_devices "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.list_devices>` to enumerate them. An "
"optional ``where`` predicate allows client-side filtering."
msgstr ""
"Los dispositivos se representan mediante modelos "
":class:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.Device` que contienen el código"
" del dispositivo, el número de cúbits, el tipo de hardware y el estado. "
"Use :meth:`SpeQtrum.list_devices "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.list_devices>` para enumerarlos. Un "
"predicado ``where`` opcional permite el filtrado en el lado del cliente."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:72
msgid "Remote Jobs"
msgstr "Trabajos Remotos"

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:74
msgid ""
":meth:`SpeQtrum.list_jobs <qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.list_jobs>`"
" returns lightweight :class:`JobInfo "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.JobInfo>` records. The ``where`` "
"predicate works the same way as with devices."
msgstr ""
":meth:`SpeQtrum.list_jobs <qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.list_jobs>`"
" devuelve registros ligeros :class:`JobInfo "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.JobInfo>`. El predicado ``where`` "
"funciona de la misma manera que con los dispositivos."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:88
msgid ""
"To inspect complete job metadata (payload, result, logs, decoded errors) "
"call :meth:`SpeQtrum.get_job "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.get_job>`. Binary fields are returned"
" as decoded strings or structured "
":class:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.ExecuteResult` objects."
msgstr ""
"Para inspeccionar los metadatos completos de un trabajo (carga útil, "
"resultado, registros, errores decodificados) llame a "
":meth:`SpeQtrum.get_job <qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.get_job>`. "
"Los campos binarios se devuelven como cadenas decodificadas u objetos "
":class:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.ExecuteResult` estructurados."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:92
msgid ""
"When you wait on a :class:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.JobHandle`, "
"the returned object is a "
":class:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.TypedJobDetail` that exposes a "
"strongly typed "
":meth:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.TypedJobDetail.get_results` "
"helper."
msgstr ""
"Cuando se espera a un "
":class:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.JobHandle`, el objeto devuelto "
"es un :class:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.TypedJobDetail` que "
"expone un auxiliar con tipado fuerte "
":meth:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.TypedJobDetail.get_results`."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:102
msgid ""
"You can still call :meth:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.get_job` "
"with a bare integer identifier. In that case a regular :class:`JobDetail "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.JobDetail>` object is returned and you "
"can inspect the individual ``*.result`` fields manually when needed."
msgstr ""
"Aún puede llamar a :meth:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.get_job` "
"con un identificador entero simple. En ese caso se devuelve un objeto "
"regular :class:`JobDetail <qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.JobDetail>` y"
" puede inspeccionar manualmente los campos ``*.result`` individuales "
"cuando sea necesario."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:107
msgid "Waiting for Completion"
msgstr "Espera de Finalización"

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:109
msgid ""
"Use :meth:`SpeQtrum.wait_for_job "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.wait_for_job>` to poll until a job "
"reaches a terminal state (``completed``, ``error``, or ``cancelled``). "
"Passing a :class:`JobHandle <qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.JobHandle>`"
" yields a :class:`TypedJobDetail "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.TypedJobDetail>` with typed result "
"access, while raw integer identifiers continue to return a plain "
":class:`JobDetail <qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.JobDetail>`. The "
"helper raises a :class:`TimeoutError` if the optional timeout elapses "
"first."
msgstr ""
"Use :meth:`SpeQtrum.wait_for_job "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.wait_for_job>` para sondear hasta que"
" un trabajo alcance un estado terminal (``completed``, ``error`` o "
"``cancelled``). Pasar un :class:`JobHandle "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.JobHandle>` produce un "
":class:`TypedJobDetail <qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.TypedJobDetail>`"
" con acceso tipado a los resultados, mientras que los identificadores "
"enteros simples continúan devolviendo un :class:`JobDetail "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum_models.JobDetail>` simple. El auxiliar lanza "
"un :class:`TimeoutError` si el tiempo de espera opcional expira primero."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:117
msgid "Functional Submission"
msgstr "Envío de Funcionales"

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:119
msgid ""
"SpeQtrum accepts the same primitive functionals used by local backends. "
"The :meth:`SpeQtrum.submit <qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.submit>` "
"method inspects the functional type and serializes the correct payload. "
"You must supply a ``device`` argument with the device code obtained from "
":meth:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.list_devices`."
msgstr ""
"SpeQtrum acepta los mismos funcionales primitivos utilizados por los "
"backends locales. El método :meth:`SpeQtrum.submit "
"<qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.submit>` inspecciona el tipo de "
"funcional y serializa la carga útil correcta. Debe proporcionar un "
"argumento ``device`` con el código de dispositivo obtenido de "
":meth:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.speqtrum.SpeQtrum.list_devices`."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:147
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Physical QPUs currently do not support analog functionals built on "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution`; for now, "
"analog hardware can run only pulse experiments from "
":mod:`~qilisdk.experiments`."
msgstr ""
"Las QPUs físicas actualmente no soportan funcionales analógicos basados "
"en :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution`; por "
"ahora, el hardware analógico solo puede ejecutar experimentos de pulso de"
" :mod:`~qilisdk.speqtrum.experiments`."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:152
msgid "Variational Programs"
msgstr "Programas Variacionales"

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:154
msgid ""
"Hybrid optimization is handled through the same "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program.VariationalProgram` "
"functional used with local backends. Serialize the fully-configured "
"variational program (ansatz, optimizer, cost function) and submit it as "
"any other functional."
msgstr ""
"La optimización híbrida se gestiona mediante el mismo funcional "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program.VariationalProgram` "
"utilizado con los backends locales. Serialice el programa variacional "
"completamente configurado (ansatz, optimizador, función de coste) y "
"envíelo como cualquier otro funcional."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:194
msgid "Pulse Experiments"
msgstr "Experimentos de Pulso"

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:196
msgid ""
"The SpeQtrum client also supports calibration-style experiments defined "
"in :mod:`qilisdk.experiments.experiment_functional`. These functional "
"objects mirror the interfaces described in the "
":doc:`/modules/functionals/functionals` chapter and return rich result "
"types."
msgstr ""
"El cliente SpeQtrum también admite experimentos de estilo de calibración "
"definidos en :mod:`qilisdk.experiments.experiment_functional`. Estos "
"objetos funcionales reflejan las interfaces descritas en el capítulo "
":doc:`/modules/functionals/functionals` y devuelven tipos de resultado "
"enriquecidos."

#: ../../modules/speqtrum/speqtrum.rst:223
msgid ""
"The resulting "
":class:`~qilisdk.experiments.experiment_result.RabiExperimentResult` and "
":class:`~qilisdk.experiments.experiment_result.T1ExperimentResult` "
"objects can then be used directly."
msgstr ""
"Los objetos "
":class:`~qilisdk.experiments.experiment_result.RabiExperimentResult` y "
":class:`~qilisdk.experiments.experiment_result.T1ExperimentResult` "
"resultantes pueden usarse directamente."

